						<h1 class='mt-14 font-GilroySemibold text-4xl/tight text-white'>
							Open-source Git client
							<!-- -->
							<span class='text-sky-300'>for macOS minimalists</span>
						</h1>
						<p class='mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-300 font-GilroyRegular'>
							Commit is a lightweight Git client you can open from anywhere any
							time you’re ready to commit your work with a single keyboard
							shortcut. It’s fast, beautiful, and completely unnecessary.
						</p>
						<form class='relative isolate mt-8 flex items-center pr-1'>
							<label for=':S3:' class='sr-only'>Email address</label><input required='' type='email'
								autocomplete='email' id=':S3:' placeholder='Email address'
								class='peer w-0 flex-auto bg-transparent px-4 py-2.5 text-base text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:outline-hidden sm:text-[0.8125rem]/6'
